0:27:47,732 --> 0:27:53,4
WHICH MAKES IT POSSIBLE
FOR THE KILLERS TO COMMIT
THEIR CRIMES.


337
0:27:53,4 --> 0:27:55,73
I WOULD ADD
THAT IT'S THE BELIEF


338
0:27:55,73 --> 0:27:57,575
THAT THOSE OTHERS
ARE DANGEROUS ENEMIES


339
0:27:57,575 --> 0:28:10,21
WHICH INSPIRES THE PERPETRATORS
TO KILL WITH SUCH ZEAL.


340
0:28:10,21 --> 0:28:13,24
YEARS AGO, I ENCOUNTERED
AN EPISODE OF THE HOLOCAUST


341
0:28:13,24 --> 0:28:17,28
WHICH SPOKE VOLUMES
ABOUT THE WILLFULNESS
AND DEDICATION OF THE KILLERS,


342
0:28:17,28 --> 0:28:22,33
AND I GOT TO KNOW ONE OF
