343
0:28:22,33 --> 0:28:26,537
I HAVE A MAP HERE
WITH ME WHICH ACTUALLY
OUTLINES THE ROUTE


344
0:28:26,537 --> 0:28:30,41
FROM HELMBRECHT
TO VOLARY...


345
0:28:30,41 --> 0:28:33,44
Goldhagen, voice-over:
IN THE LAST MONTHS
OF WORLD WAR II,


346
0:28:33,44 --> 0:28:37,548
AS THE ALLIED FORCES NEARED
THE CONCENTRATION CAMPS
HOUSING JEWS AND OTHERS,


347
0:28:37,548 --> 0:28:40,518
GERMANS EMPTIED THEIR CAMPS
AND DROVE THEIR PRISONERS


348
0:28:40,518 --> 0:28:44,522
ON FORCED MARCHES
THROUGH THE NEARBY TOWNS
AND COUNTRYSIDE.


349
0:28:44,522 --> 0:28:46,23
[SILBIGER SPEAKING GERMAN]


350
0:28:46,23 --> 0:28:50,27
Goldhagen: THE DEATH MARCHES
LEFT A TRAIL OF CORPSES
IN THEIR WAKE,


351
0:28:50,27 --> 0:28:53,531
AND THE MARCHING PRISONERS WERE
DESCRIBED BY MORE THAN
ONE WITNESS


352
0:28:53,531 --> 0:28:56,1
AS "THE WALKING DEAD."


353
0:28:56,1 --> 0:28:59,103
THESE ARE ACTUAL PHOTOS
OF THE YOUNG WOMEN


354
0:28:59,103 --> 0:29:13,751
WHO WERE WITH LILLI
ON THE MARCH.


355
0:29:13,751 --> 0:29:17,755
ON THE SUMMER DAY
LILY REVISITED THE ROUTE
OF A DEATH MARCH WITH ME,


356
0:29:17,755 --> 0:29:20,758
THE COUNTRYSIDE WAS BEAUTIFUL.


357
0:29:20,758 --> 0:29:28,766
BUT IN THE SPRING OF 1945,
IT WAS COLD AND BLEAK.


358
0:29:28,766 --> 0:29:33,771
LILY'S GUARDS ACTUALLY HAD
RECEIVED EXPLICIT ORDERS
NOT TO KILL ANY MORE JEWS,


359
0:29:33,771 --> 0:29:37,275
BUT THEY WILLFULLY DEFIED
THEIR SUPERIORS.


360
0:29:37,275 --> 0:29:40,778
THEY DROVE HER AND THE OTHERS,
STARVING, WEARING NOTHING
MORE THAN RAGS,


361
0:29:40,778 --> 0:29:44,148
DAY AFTER DAY THROUGH
THE FRIGID COUNTRYSIDE.


362
0:29:44,148 --> 0:29:47,852
SOMETIMES WE WOULDN'T
EVEN GET FOOD FOR
24 HOURS, FOR 48 HOURS.


363
0:29:47,852 --> 0:29:50,855
PEOPLE RESORTED
TO ANYTHING
THAT WAS FOUND


364
0:29:50,855 --> 0:29:54,358
OR ANYTHING ROTTEN THAT
WAS--YOU KNOW, YOU JUST
GRABBED AT ANYTHING.


365
0:29:54,358 --> 0:29:54,358
AND YOU WERE 16
AT THE TIME?


366
0:29:54,358 --> 0:29:57,361
YEAH.


367
0:29:57,361 --> 0:30:1,966
AND IN ONE PLACE,
SOMEONE BROKE
INTO A PANTRY


368
0:30:1,966 --> 0:30:5,97
OR SOMEPLACE WHERE
WE ARRIVED AND STOLE
SOME LOAFS OF BREAD.


369
0:30:5,97 --> 0:30:9,974
AND FOR THAT,
THEY SELECTED 50 GIRLS
AND KILLED THEM


370
0:30:9,974 --> 0:30:12,477
OVER THE MASS GRAVE
THERE.


371
0:30:12,477 --> 0:30:16,981
WE HAD TO COME BACK
AND COVER THEM,


372
0:30:16,981 --> 0:30:20,985
AND THERE WERE MANY
OF THEM STILL ALIVE
WHEN WE HAD TO DO THAT.


373
0:30:20,985 --> 0:30:23,988
SO THEY--YOU HAD
TO HELP BURY THEM ALIVE?


374
0:30:23,988 --> 0:30:26,491
WE HAD TO DO--
WE HAD TO PUT--


375
0:30:26,491 --> 0:30:29,494
YES, THE EARTH,
COVER THEM WITH EARTH.


376
0:30:29,494 --> 0:30:34,499
SO THIS WAS
THE BIGGEST HORRIBLE...


377
0:30:34,499 --> 0:30:38,503
[VOICE CRACKS]
YEAH....


378
0:30:38,503 --> 0:30:41,506
PERIOD.


379
0:30:41,506 --> 0:30:47,411
[DISTANT ROLLING THUNDER]


380
0:30:47,411 --> 0:30:52,416
ONE OF THE ASTONISHING THINGS
IS THAT THEY WERE MARCHING
THE JEWISH PRISONERS


381
0:30:52,416 --> 0:30:55,386
LITERALLY THE LAST DAY
OF THE WAR.


382
0:30:55,386 --> 0:30:58,389
INSTEAD OF RUNNING AWAY
TO AVOID CAPTURE, THEY
STAYED WITH THE PRISONERS,


383
0:30:58,389 --> 0:30:58,389
THEY CONTINUED
TO DENY THEM FOOD...


384
0:30:58,389 --> 0:31:0,825
ABSOLUTELY.


385
0:31:0,825 --> 0:31:3,761
THEY CONTINUED TO BEAT THEM,
THEY CONTINUED TO KILL THEM,


386
0:31:3,761 --> 0:31:10,368
THEY CONTINUED TO DO IT
TO THE VERY END.


387
0:31:10,368 --> 0:31:12,503
WE KNEW THE RUSSIANS
WERE CLOSING IN THERE,


388
0:31:12,503 --> 0:31:14,505
AND THEN WE HEARD
ARTILLERY,


389
0:31:14,505 --> 0:31:17,341
SOME PLANES FLYING
OVERHEAD,


390
0:31:17,341 --> 0:31:19,343
HEARD SOME BOMBINGS
IN THE DISTANCE,


391
0:31:19,343 --> 0:31:23,47
SO WE KNEW
THEY WERE VERY CLOSE.


392
0:31:23,47 --> 0:31:28,553
[EXPLOSIONS, GUNFIRE]


393
0:31:28,553 --> 0:31:33,57
THEY MANAGED FOR SUCH
A LONG TIME TO KEEP
AHEAD OF THE ALLIES,


394
0:31:33,57 --> 0:31:36,227
GOING NOWHERE, YOU KNOW,
TO--A PLACE--TO NOWHERE.


395
0:31:36,227 --> 0:31:39,23
JUST TO DRAG US,
JUST TO...


396
0:31:39,23 --> 0:31:42,233
JUST GO IN CIRCLES,
ACTUALLY. THAT'S WHAT
WAS HAPPENING.


397
0:31:42,233 --> 0:31:45,736
THEY DIDN'T KNOW
THEMSELVES WHAT THEY
WERE DOING.


398
0:31:45,736 --> 0:31:49,74
THEY COULD HAVE EASILY
LEFT US WHEREVER WE WERE


399
0:31:49,74 --> 0:31:52,109
AND JUST DISAPPEAR,
AND THEY DIDN'T.


400
0:31:52,109 --> 0:31:56,113
THEY BELIEVED THE JEWS
WERE EVIL INCARNATE,
AN ENEMY OF HUMANKIND,


401
0:31:56,113 --> 0:32:0,551
A THREAT TO
THE WELL-BEING AND FUTURE
EXISTENCE OF GERMANY.


402
0:32:0,551 --> 0:32:2,553
AND IF YOU BELIEVE THAT,


403
0:32:2,553 --> 0:32:5,623
JUST AS IF YOU BELIEVE
SOMEONE'S ABOUT
TO ATTACK YOUR CHILD,


404
0:32:5,623 --> 0:32:9,126
YOU WILL DO
ANYTHING YOU CAN.


405
0:32:9,126 --> 0:32:11,262
YEAH.


406
0:32:11,262 --> 0:32:13,264
[CAR HORN HONKS]


407
0:32:13,264 --> 0:32:18,269
EACH OF US TRIES TO MAKE SENSE
OF THE HORRORS IN HIS
OR HER OWN WAY.


408
0:32:18,269 --> 0:32:22,807
OVER THE YEARS, I HAVE TALKED
WITH MANY WHO GRAPPLE
OVER THESE ISSUES,


409
0:32:22,807 --> 0:32:26,31
BUT NEVER ONE MORE THOUGHTFUL
THAN A MAN I MET IN RWANDA--


410
0:32:26,31 --> 0:32:30,314
THARCISSE KARUGARAMA,
THE COUNTRY'S MINISTER
OF JUSTICE.


