1436
1:38:22,462 --> 1:38:25,499
EACH OF THE MEMBERS MUST HAVE
THE RIGHT TO INTERVENE


1437
1:38:25,499 --> 1:38:27,534
INDIVIDUALLY OR COLLECTIVELY


1438
1:38:27,534 --> 1:38:30,704
TO STOP CAMPAIGNS
OF ELIMINATION,


1439
1:38:30,704 --> 1:38:33,774
BUT INTERVENTION,
EVEN FORCEFUL INTERVENTION,


1440
1:38:33,774 --> 1:38:35,375
IS NOT ENOUGH.


