1443
1:38:39,947 --> 1:38:43,617
WE NEED AN EFFECTIVE SYSTEM
OF PREVENTION.


1444
1:38:43,617 --> 1:38:46,353
WE'VE GOT TO STOP GENOCIDES
BEFORE THEY HAPPEN


1445
1:38:46,353 --> 1:38:48,889
