1:38:53,493 --> 1:38:56,196
THE U.S. HAS A BOUNTY PROGRAM
FOR GETTING PEOPLE


1448
1:38:56,196 --> 1:38:58,31
TO HUNT DOWN TERRORISTS.


1449
1:38:58,31 --> 1:39:0,167
WHY NOT HAVE
DEMOCRATIC COUNTRIES DO THE SAME


1450
1:39:0,167 --> 1:39:3,804
FOR LEADERS WHO PERPETRATE
