1:39:34,267 --> 1:39:38,939
THE INTERNATIONAL
COMMUNITY IS IN LOVE
WITH THE STATUS QUO.


1463
1:39:38,939 --> 1:39:42,509
WE MUST SHOW
THAT IT DOESN'T PAY.


1464
1:39:42,509 --> 1:39:48,248
IF PEOPLE KNEW
THAT AT THE END
OF THE DAY


1465
1:39:48,248 --> 1:39:50,517
THEY'D BE
THE LOSERS,


1466
1:39:50,517 --> 1:39:53,286
THEY WOULD
NEVER INVEST


