1:39:53,286 --> 1:39:55,188
IN A LOSING
ENTERPRISE.


1468
1:39:55,188 --> 1:39:57,391
IT'S BECAUSE
GENOCIDE IS
A POLITICAL GAME,


1469
1:39:57,391 --> 1:39:59,526
IT'S A POWER PLAY,
