1:40:7,3 --> 1:40:8,802
THEY'D BE
THE LOSERS,


1473
1:40:8,802 --> 1:40:13,674
THEY WOULD NOT
PLAY THE GAME,
THAT'S FOR SURE.


1474
1:40:13,674 --> 1:40:15,409
Goldhagen: WHAT IS
THE ALTERNATIVE TO DEALING


