1479
1:40:30,323 --> 1:40:34,361
THE KEY TO GETTING US TO ACT IS
TO IDENTIFY WITH THE VICTIMS,


1480
1:40:34,361 --> 1:40:36,663
TO THINK OF EACH ONE
