1:40:51,878 --> 1:40:54,614
AT THE PLACE WHERE HIS BEGAN.


1487
1:40:54,614 --> 1:40:59,319
SHORTLY AFTER THE GERMANS
AND THE ROMANIAN ALLIES
ENTERED MY FATHER'S TOWN,


1488
1:40:59,319 --> 1:41:1,888
THEY SLAUGHTERED 800 JEWS.


1489
1:41:1,888 --> 1:41:4,558
MY FATHER AND HIS FAMILY
WERE NEARLY EXECUTED


1490
1:41:4,558 --> 1:41:6,96
ON A DIRT ROAD
BEHIND THEIR HOUSE


1491
1:41:6,96 --> 1:41:12,766
SOMEWHERE IN THIS NEIGHBORHOOD.


1492
1:41:12,766 --> 1:41:13,834
DO YOU SEE
ANY TRACKS?


1493
1:41:13,834 --> 1:41:16,336
THEY SHOULD BE
STRAIGHT AHEAD.


