1:41:16,336 --> 1:41:18,205
IF WE END HERE,
THE TRACKS SHOULD
BE RIGHT DOWN HERE.


1495
1:41:18,205 --> 1:41:20,941
HERE THEY ARE.


1496
1:41:20,941 --> 1:41:22,342
TATI, SEE
THE TRACKS?


1497
1:41:22,342 --> 1:41:23,677
I DON'T KNOW.
DO YOU SEE THEM?


1498
1:41:23,677 --> 1:41:24,911
YES, THEY'RE
RIGHT THERE.


1499
1:41:24,911 --> 1:41:26,88
OH, I SEE.
YEAH. THAT WAS HERE.


1500
1:41:26,88 --> 1:41:34,621
I LIVED RIGHT HERE.


1501
1:41:34,621 --> 1:41:37,924
I RAN OUT WITH MY
FATHER BEYOND
FROM THERE.


1502
1:41:37,924 --> 1:41:39,25
OUT THE OTHER SIDE?


1503
1:41:39,25 --> 1:41:41,361
YES. I REMEMBER WE
RAN OVER A FENCE,


1504
1:41:41,361 --> 1:41:43,363
AND AS WE WERE
RUNNING, A SOLDIER
SPIED US


1505
1:41:43,363 --> 1:41:44,831
AND BEAT MY FATHER
VERY SEVERELY


1506
1:41:44,831 --> 1:41:46,333
WITH THE BUTT
OF HIS RIFLE


1507
1:41:46,333 --> 1:41:48,101
AND PUT US AGAINST--
SAID, "WAIT HERE,"


1508
1:41:48,101 --> 1:41:50,637
PUT US AGAINST--
OF COURSE THERE
WAS A FENCE--


1509
1:41:50,637 --> 1:41:52,139
AGAINST THE FENCE,


1510
1:41:52,139 --> 1:41:58,845
AND THEN HE TOLD ME
TO TELL THE FAMILY
TO COME--


1511
1:41:58,845 --> 1:41:59,846
TO COME OUT.


1512
1:41:59,846 --> 1:42:0,847
SO HE SENT YOU BACK
TO THE HOUSE?


1513
1:42:0,847 --> 1:42:2,215
HE SENT ME
BACK TO THE HOUSE,


1514
1:42:2,215 --> 1:42:7,387
AND WE SAW NEIGHBORS
STANDING BEYOND
THIS RAILWAY,


1515
1:42:7,387 --> 1:42:10,39
AND WE REALIZED
THAT THEY'RE
LOOKING AT US


1516
1:42:10,39 --> 1:42:14,995
IN A CERTAIN WAY
THAT THEY--
IN AN OMINOUS WAY.


1517
1:42:14,995 --> 1:42:24,7
THEY--WHICH DIDN'T--
WHICH DIDN'T BODE WELL,
TO SAY THE LEAST.


1518
1:42:24,7 --> 1:42:26,94
NOW THAT WE'RE HERE,
IS THIS--HAS IT
CHANGED YOUR VIEW?


1519
1:42:26,94 --> 1:42:29,509
YOU SEE, THE POINT IS
THAT THE SCHOLARLY ELEMENT--


1520
1:42:29,509 --> 1:42:33,68
THE SCHOLAR WITHIN ME
IMMEDIATELY TAKES OVER THE--


1521
1:42:33,68 --> 1:42:38,985
AND OVERSHADOWS
THE EMOTIONS
OF THE SURVIVOR


1522
1:42:38,985 --> 1:42:42,622
WHO REVISITS THE SCENE
OF HIS NEAR DEATH.


1523
1:42:42,622 --> 1:42:46,86
SO AS I TALK TO YOU,
I BEGIN TO REFLECT,


1524
1:42:46,86 --> 1:42:49,95
DRAW HISTORICAL ANALOGIES,
AND SO ON,


1525
1:42:49,95 --> 1:42:52,332
SO THEREFORE,
IT HAS A CERTAIN
TEMPERING EFFECT


1526
1:42:52,332 --> 1:42:54,501
UPON MY EMOTIONS
AS I CONFRONT


1527
1:42:54,501 --> 1:42:56,2
THIS HOUSE WHERE I LIVED,


1528
1:42:56,2 --> 1:42:57,571
THIS STREET
WHERE I WALKED,


1529
1:42:57,571 --> 1:43:3,109
AND REFLECTED ON MY BLOOD
LYING IN THE DUST HERE,


1530
1:43:3,109 --> 1:43:6,58
BUT WHEN I REMEMBER
THAT MOMENT
AS I WALKED


1531
1:43:6,58 --> 1:43:8,315
AND I JUST COULDN'T
BELIEVE--


1532
1:43:8,315 --> 1:43:12,485
YES, I DID REFLECT
UPON HOW I WOULD LIE DEAD.


1533
1:43:12,485 --> 1:43:14,821
WHAT DOES IT MEAN
TO BE DEAD


1534
1:43:14,821 --> 1:43:17,357
AND TO LIE
IN YOUR BLOOD?


1535
1:43:17,357 --> 1:43:39,346
I REMEMBERED VIVIDLY
THIS IMAGERY THAT I HAD
AS I WALKED, AND...


1536
1:43:39,346 --> 1:43:41,882
Goldhagen, voice-over:
WHAT MUST IT FEEL LIKE
FOR A 10-YEAR-OLD BOY


1537
1:43:41,882 --> 1:43:47,22
TO CONTEMPLATE HIS OWN
IMMINENT, VIOLENT DEATH


1538
1:43:47,22 --> 1:43:53,36
OR A 16-YEAR-OLD GIRL
OR A 19-YEAR-OLD MAN?


1539
1:43:53,36 --> 1:43:57,63
WHAT MUST IT FEEL LIKE
TO BE IMPRISONED IN A RAPE CAMP


1540
1:43:57,63 --> 1:44:1,268
OR TO WATCH HELPLESSLY
