1:44:1,268 --> 1:44:12,979
OR AS YOUR PEOPLE
ARE DECIMATED?


1542
1:44:12,979 --> 1:44:15,982
WHAT MUST IT HAVE BEEN LIKE
FOR THE MEN OF SREBRENICA


1543
1:44:15,982 --> 1:44:19,686
WHO WERE HERDED
INTO THIS WAREHOUSE


1544
1:44:19,686 --> 1:44:21,988
OR FOR THE OTHERS
