[GUNSHOT]


1550
1:45:12,539 --> 1:45:17,21
[GUNSHOT]


1551
1:45:17,21 --> 1:45:21,14
[RAPID GUNSHOTS]


1552
1:45:21,14 --> 1:45:32,859
[GUNFIRE CONTINUING]


1553
1:45:32,859 --> 1:45:39,432
[GUNFIRE CONTINUING]


1554
1:45:39,432 --> 1:45:42,402
Goldhagen: WE CAN'T
STAND BY ANYMORE.


1555
1:45:42,402 --> 1:45:45,905
PEOPLE ARE DYING EVERY DAY.


1556
1:45:45,905 --> 1:45:48,708
A FEW POLITICAL LEADERS
START GENOCIDES.


1557
1:45:48,708 --> 1:45:53,13
A FEW POLITICAL LEADERS
