1560
1:45:59,152 --> 1:46:4,958
POTENTIAL MASS KILLERS MAKE.


1561
1:46:4,958 --> 1:46:8,28
WE MUST HOLD OUR LEADERS
ACCOUNTABLE AND DEMAND


1562
1:46:8,28 --> 1:46:29,315
THAT THEY BRING AN END
